flowchart TD
    A[Bootstrap complete] --> B[Interpretation Phase<br/>Orchestrator + Architect]

    B --> C[Architect formalises Initial DECOR<br/>decor.md + metadata]
    C --> D[Orchestrator initialises Ticket Map<br/>tickets, sequencing, metadata]
    D --> E[Architect applies DECOR grounding strategy<br/>within Interpretation]

    E --> F[Implementation Phase<br/>Orchestrator + Implementer]
    F --> G[Ticket Loop Workflow<br/>sequential ticket execution]

    G --> H[Reconciliation Phase<br/>Auditor + Architect + Orchestrator]
    H --> I[Drift classification<br/>DECOR updates formalised]
    I --> J[Reconciled DECOR produced]
    J --> K[Verification Phase<br/>Verifier]
    K --> L[Run golden, dark, governance, replay tests]

    L --> M{All verification checks pass?}
    M -- No --> H
    M -- Yes --> N[Closure Phase<br/>Orchestrator + Curator]

    N --> O[Closure actions<br/>closure report, archival]
    O --> P[Tranche closed]
